  <brief_title>Evaluation of the Pharmacokinetics, Safety, and Tolerability of TPM XR as Adjunctive Therapy in Pediatric Subjects With Epilepsy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of the Pharmacokinetics, Safety, and Tolerability of TPM XR as Adjunctive Therapy in Pediatric Subjects With Epilepsy</official_title>
