  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Multidose, Open-label, Multi-center Study to examine the steady state pharmacokinetics of TPM
      XR, as well as, safety and tolerability of repeated oral dosing in pediatric subjects with
      epilepsy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
